Honolulu.Salvation Army Wai\u02bboli Tea Room: Salvation Army Waiʻoli Tea Room has been closed since December 30, 2014, and is located at 2950 Mānoa Road, at the intersection of Oahu Avenue, in the City and County of Honolulu, on the island of Oahu, in the U.S. state of Hawaii. It was added to National Register of Historic Places listings on Oahu on October 30, 1998. It currently operates under the name Waiʻoli Tea Room & Bakery.
